## 8. Import (brownfield)

```bash
terraform import aws_s3_bucket.logs my-bucket-name
terraform import aws_instance.app i-0abc123456789abcd
terraform import aws_security_group.web sg-0abc123456789abcd
```

Write the **`resource`** block first; import only updates **state**. Run **`plan`** after to fix attribute drift.

