## 9. Commands (day-to-day)

| Command | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `terraform init` | Providers + backend |
| `terraform init -upgrade` | Bump providers within constraints |
| `terraform validate` | Syntax check |
| `terraform fmt -recursive` | Format `.tf` |
| `terraform plan` | Preview changes |
| `terraform apply` | Apply |
| `terraform apply -target=RES` | Emergency partial (avoid habit) |
| `terraform destroy` | Delete tracked resources |
| `terraform state list` / `state show` | Inspect state |
| `terraform state rm` | Drop from state (does not delete cloud — dangerous) |
| `terraform output` | Print outputs |
| `terraform workspace list` | If using workspaces |
| `terraform providers` | Locked versions |

